     first create a reclassified of the original (e.g., using the
     GRASS tool reclass) which contains only the desired
     categories, and then use the reclassed as input to Grandom.

SEE ALSO
     random[1], reclass[1]

AUTHOR
     Dr. James Hinthorne, GIS Lab, Central Washington University














































